import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]

    plt.hist(data['price'], bins=30, color='blue', alpha=0.7, label='Price')
    plt.axvline(data['price'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['price'].median():.2f}")
    
    plt.xlabel('Price')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of price?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    avg_prices = data.groupby('symbol')['price'].mean().reset_index()
    
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.bar(avg_prices['symbol'], avg_prices['price'])
    
    plt.title('What is the average price by symbol?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Symbol')
    plt.ylabel('Average Price')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]

    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    scatter = ax.scatter(data['symbol'], data['price'], c=data['price'], cmap='viridis')
    ax.set_xlabel('Symbol')
    ax.set_ylabel('Price')
    ax.set_title('What is the correlation between symbol and price?')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    legend1 = ax.legend(*scatter.legend_elements(), title="Prices")
    ax.add_artist(legend1)

    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    symbol_counts = data['symbol'].value_counts()
    ax = symbol_counts.plot(kind='bar', color='c')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of symbols?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Symbols')
    plt.ylabel('Count')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend(['Symbol Frequency'])
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
